| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-1035 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhouse)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 59c043a5-8c08-5fdb-b264-9546e75f3722"
